<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Gdata_App calls the Zend_Http_Client::setCookie method to set cookies on the client object for use in future requests.  While the GData services send the cookies without any URL encoding, the setCookie method encodes the cookie values.  This leads to future 'Cookie' headers being sent to the GData services with values the server cannot interpret.</p>

    </div>
